table_caption: List of spatial regions from the cluster showing significant correlation with self-reported fatigue among COVID individuals.The regions from PRN which demonstrated significant correlation are presented with peak MNI coordinates (X Y Z) and corresponding peak t-score values for each cluster. Keys: FC = Functional Connectivity; ftg. = Fatigue Scores, Cl. = Cluster; Cl. No. = Number of Clusters; Cl. Size = Cluster Size; t = peak t-score; pFDR = false discovery rate corrected p-value.
